</div></div></section><section class="nha-section nha-primary-bg nha-school-pattern  nha-story-spotlight-component nha-large-story-spotlight" style="" aria-label="Spotlight: Student Government Officers Pledge to Uphold Tradition of Excellence"><div class="nha-large-story-spotlight-image nha-tag-border"><div class="nha-large-story-spotlight-image-wrap lazy-load-image" data-src="url('/getmedia/03859463-0aea-4f92-b93f-208ff777ea08/Riverton_StudentGovernment_992x558.jpg?width=992&amp;height=558&amp;ext=.jpg')"><img data-src="/getmedia/03859463-0aea-4f92-b93f-208ff777ea08/Riverton_StudentGovernment_992x558.jpg?width=992&amp;height=558&amp;ext=.jpg" alt="Student government officers" class="lazy-load-image"></div></div>
