<h2>Tour the School</h2>
<p>We would love to show you our world so contact us to schedule a tour. We also hold open houses where you can meet our amazing teachers.</p>
<a href="mailto:89.TWILLIAMS@nhaschools.com?subject=Tour&amp;body=" class="nha-btn nha-btn-wide nha-btn-primary">Tour the School</a>
</div></div>
